sequenceDiagram
    participant S as idc host<br/>10.20.0.60
    participant IG as wireguard-gw-idc<br/>10.20.0.10 / wg0 .2
    participant CG as wireguard-gw<br/>wg0 .1 / 10.10.0.10
    participant D as company target<br/>10.10.0.50:9090

    S->>IG: dst 10.10.0.50 (static route via 10.20.0.10)
    IG->>CG: WireGuard UDP/51820 to 203.0.113.10 (direct, no FortiGate)
